trans-unit.source: Provides static methods and properties for <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.VBArrayObject" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.VBArrayObject" /> 物件提供靜態方法和屬性。

trans-unit.source: All methods of this class are called by passing in a reference to the object that is requesting access to the method.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別的所有方法都是透過將參考傳入要求存取方法的物件來進行呼叫。

trans-unit.source: This class belongs to the built-in object model category.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別屬於內建物件模型分類。

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to a prototype-based object that is using this prototype.
trans-unit.target: 取得使用這個原型之原型架構物件的參考。

trans-unit.source: A reference to a prototype-based object.
trans-unit.target: 原型架構物件的參考。

trans-unit.source: The object that this method is acting upon.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法執行位置的物件。

trans-unit.source: Determines the number of dimensions in the specified array.
trans-unit.target: 判斷指定陣列中的維度數目。

trans-unit.source: The number of dimensions in <paramref name="thisob" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="thisob" /> 中的維度數目。

trans-unit.source: The object that this method is acting upon.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法執行位置的物件。

trans-unit.source: An array that represents the indexes of each dimension that specifies the position of the element to get.
trans-unit.target: 陣列，表示每個維度的索引，指定要取得之元素的位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets the value at the specified position in the specified array.
trans-unit.target: 取得位於指定陣列中之指定位置的值。

trans-unit.source: The value at the specified position in <paramref name="thisob" />.
trans-unit.target: 位於 <paramref name="thisob" /> 中之指定位置的值。

trans-unit.source: If `thisob` has three or fewer dimensions, `args` can contain a comma-separated list of indexes.
trans-unit.target: 如果`thisob`有三個或更少的維度，`args`可包含以逗號分隔清單的索引。

trans-unit.source: If `thisob` has four or more dimensions, `args` can contain an array of indexes.
trans-unit.target: 如果`thisob`有四個或多個維度，`args`可以包含索引的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The object that this method is acting upon.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法執行位置的物件。

trans-unit.source: The dimension whose lower bound is determined.
trans-unit.target: 下限已決定的維度。

trans-unit.source: Gets the lower bound of the specified dimension in the specified array.
trans-unit.target: 取得指定陣列中指定之維度的下限。

trans-unit.source: The lower bound of <paramref name="dimension" /> in <paramref name="thisob" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="dimension" /> 中 <paramref name="thisob" /> 的下限。

trans-unit.source: The object that this method is acting upon.

trans-unit.target: 指令碼引擎的參考。

trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.VBArrayObject" /> 物件轉換成 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.ArrayObject" /> 物件。
